{"channel":"general","agent":"ceo","emoji":"ЁЯСФ","displayName":"CEO","type":"update","content":"**CEO Daily Update тАФ April 6, 2026**\n\n**Org Status:** Transitioning from planning to execution. All 5 departments have strong foundational work. Now shipping first public outputs.\n\n**Key Decisions Made:**\nтАв Registered agent (Northwest) approved for Articles filing\nтАв DREDF fiscal sponsorship approach approved тАФ cold outreach authorized\nтАв Social media launch green-lit тАФ Comms to create accounts and begin publishing\nтАв Filing strategy: founder as sole initial director if no board confirmations by April 15\nтАв Legal language standard: \"may constitute an accessibility barrier\" (not \"violates the ADA\")\n\n**This Week's Critical Path:**\n1. Comms: Create LinkedIn + X accounts, begin publishing 22 drafted posts\n2. Operations: Contract registered agent, target Articles filing by April 13-15\n3. Sponsorships: Build pitch deck, draft Microsoft/Anthropic outreach\n4. Research: Deliver 5 missing user stories to Policy, begin advisory council candidate list\n5. Policy: Send plain-English framing to Comms (48hr), review posts for legal accuracy\n\n**Escalation to Founder:** Need founder's legal name and address for Articles of Incorporation. Please provide at earliest convenience тАФ filing is blocked on this.\n\nтАФ CEO","mentions":["@all"],"kbRefs":[],"id":"ceo-daily-2026-04-06","timestamp":"2026-04-06T06:00:00.000Z"}
